{"type":"getPostById","data":{"title":"[教學] open-slide 使用教學","date":"2026-07-02T16:00:00.000Z","description":"<blockquote>\n<p>註記：此頁為由 AI（gpt-5-mini-2025-08-07）自動翻譯自英文原文，可能含有少量不準確之處。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1>📌 介紹</h1>\n<p>使用 open-slide 技能讓 AI 幫你快速生出一份簡報</p>","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"ai","_id":"cmr50ruh4002krx3gb8k96x13"},{"name":"skill","_id":"cmr50ruhz006trx3g8vbg64w5"}],"content":"\n    <style>\n    .post-lang-switch{\n      position: absolute;\n      top: .75rem;\n      right: .75rem;\n      z-index: 2;\n      color: var(--link, #3273dc);\n    }\n    .post-lang-switch:hover{opacity:.8}\n    </style>\n  \n    <a class=\"post-lang-switch\" href=\"/blog/tutorial-open-slide.en/\" title=\"View English version\" aria-label=\"View English version\">\n      <i class=\"fas fa-language\"></i>\n    </a>\n  <blockquote>\n<p>註記：此頁為由 AI（gpt-5-mini-2025-08-07）自動翻譯自英文原文，可能含有少量不準確之處。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1>📌 介紹</h1>\n<p>使用 open-slide 技能讓 AI 幫你快速生出一份簡報</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h1>🚀 實際操作</h1>\n<h2 id=\"Init-Demo-簡報\">Init Demo 簡報</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npx @open-slide/cli init my-demo-slide</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hsiangjenli/pic-bed/main/images/20260703192900.png\" alt=\"20260703192900\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hsiangjenli/pic-bed/main/images/20260703193024.png\" alt=\"20260703193024\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>產生一份完整的 repo，包含啟動簡報的工具、Agent Skill、範例簡報等等</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"啟動簡報\">啟動簡報</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://localhost:5173/\">http://localhost:5173/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cd my-demo-slide</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm run dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hsiangjenli/pic-bed/main/images/20260703193221.png\" alt=\"20260703193221\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hsiangjenli/pic-bed/main/images/20260703193256.png\" alt=\"20260703193256\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"經常使用到的-Skill\">經常使用到的 Skill</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code>/create-slide</code>: 用來新建或草擬 slide deck</li>\n<li><code>/apply-comments</code>: 用來處理 @slide-comment 標記</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"實際操作截圖\">實際操作截圖</h2>\n<h3 id=\"使用-create-slide-產生簡報\">使用 <code>/create-slide</code> 產生簡報</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hsiangjenli/pic-bed/main/images/20260703201640.png\" alt=\"20260703201640\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"需求問答（風格、頁數、效果等等）\">需求問答（風格、頁數、效果等等）</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hsiangjenli/pic-bed/main/images/20260703201711.png\" alt=\"20260703201711\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hsiangjenli/pic-bed/main/images/20260703201906.png\" alt=\"20260703201906\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hsiangjenli/pic-bed/main/images/20260703201821.png\" alt=\"20260703201821\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hsiangjenli/pic-bed/main/images/20260703202157.png\" alt=\"20260703202157\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"第一版產出的簡報\">第一版產出的簡報</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hsiangjenli/pic-bed/main/images/20260703211455.png\" alt=\"20260703211455\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"在簡報上留下建議\">在簡報上留下建議</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hsiangjenli/pic-bed/main/images/20260703212008.png\" alt=\"20260703212008\"></p>\n<ol>\n<li>在簡報上留下 Comment</li>\n<li>在 terminal 上執行 <code>/apply-comments</code>，就會把根據 Comment 進行的修改</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"第二版產出的簡報\">第二版產出的簡報</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hsiangjenli/pic-bed/main/images/20260703220930.png\" alt=\"20260703220930\"></p>\n<h1>🔁 重點回顧</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>使用 <code>npx @open-slide/cli init my-demo-slide</code> 產生一份完整的簡報專案</li>\n<li>使用 <code>npm run dev</code> 啟動簡報</li>\n<li>使用 <code>/create-slide</code> 產生簡報</li>\n<li>使用 <code>/apply-comments</code> 依據簡報上的 Comment 進行修改</li>\n<li>目前 open-slide 仍在開發中，僅支援匯出成 pdf、html 以及圖片</li>\n</ol>\n<h1>🔗 參考資料</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/1weiho/open-slide\">Open Slide GitHub</a></li>\n</ul>\n","_path":"/zh-TW/tutorial-open-slide/","_link":"https://hsiangjenli.github.io/blog/zh-TW/tutorial-open-slide/","_id":"cmr50ruhb003jrx3gb9v51fw1"}}